data.description:
This spacious home, with four generously sized bedrooms, is ideal for both family life and social gatherings. A serene 
 master bathroom features a garden bath for peaceful relaxation. Notable features include a newly extended lanai with vinyl 
windows, which increases the available living area, and the attic's foam insulation for year-round comfort. The property has also recently experienced a significant price reduction. The backyard is enclosed with an all-vinyl fence, offering added privacy.'
